data.description:
Come home to this private 4.85 Acre get away on the lake.  Bring your Jet ski, boat, fishing poles or just go swimming and feel like you are in your own resort.  The home is a Jacobsen built double wide home with a great floor plan and large deck.  The property also has a large gazebo with electric and lights along with a separate work shop .
Seller will pay up to $8000 in closing costs and pre-paids for buyer with a full price offer. Please give 2 hours notice for showings!
